{"tid":2419753,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"輝瑞疫苗所帶來的保護力","createTime":"2021-02-23T12:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-24T04:53:45.000Z","uid":38861,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"8538cd7148cf9e63e35234c91bce589f4e6c7702","tid":2419753,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"在中國疫苗第三期臨床數據姍姍來遲還未正式向外公開詳細資料的時候，輝瑞mRNA疫苗早已率先公開數據表示注射兩劑疫苗七日後的保護力高達95%，同時亦表示在第一劑注射後的12日之後亦具有一定的保護力。<br />\n<br />\n最近，有尚未經由同行審批的文章(Ref1)為輝端疫苗的效力再度作出統計，特別針對在第一劑注射後的效用作出研究。<br />\n<br />\n測試的人士分別有兩組，一組為注射第一劑疫苗後1-11日受到武肺感染的人士（共1755人），另一組為注射第一劑疫苗後12-28日受到武肺感染的人士（共1142人）。<br />\n<br />\n為比對疫苗所帶來的效益，研究人員找來相同地區受到武肺感染但沒有注射疫苗的同等人數作出比較。<br />\n<br />\n研究的其中一道重要發現，就是注射第一劑疫苗後12-28日受到武肺感染人士的病毒基因Ct值比沒有注射疫苗為高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyK27t0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyK27t0.png&h=be401ab2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCt值越高，病毒含量越細，亦即是代表注射第一劑疫苗後12-28日的人士就算受到感染，體內的病毒含量亦會顯著相對減低，確實的病毒含量為低出2-4倍。<br />\n而於注射第一劑疫苗後1-11日受到武肺感染的人士，其Ct值則與沒有注射疫苗的人士沒有分別。<br />\n<br />\n體內的病毒含量，一直與重病出現的機率有著正面關係。<br />\n<br />\n如今至需一劑便能量度出Ct值的下降，可見瑞輝疫苗的保護效力有著信心的保證。<br />\n<br />\n但同樣結果是否得以套用在變種病毒，文章並沒有特別說明。<br />\n<br />\nRef1: <a href=\"https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2021.02.06.21251283v1.full.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.medrxiv.org%2Fcontent%2F10.1101%2F2021.02.06.21251283v1.full.pdf&d=w4lkeVluhl8nqpRa%2FCUv34sqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=fdc2bbed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.medrxiv.org/content/10.1101/2021.02.06.21251283v1.full.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"f152e2cb7abca076c22861550ece32c7152d7c13","tid":2419753,"uid":62799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推晒啲廢老藍絲打支那疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d975c693db248543c74662ca7ecfa737cff0d350","tid":2419753,"uid":34119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"咁科興呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fc6a38f9813bf61ef44af615f6c854d89a79f20","tid":2419753,"uid":38861,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"f152e2cb7abca076c22861550ece32c7152d7c13","tid":2419753,"uid":62799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:00:11.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n推晒啲廢老藍絲打支那疫苗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"事實上老人家比較有急切性要打疫苗，不過香港政府辦事不力/急於展現愛國情懷，所以將未有充足數據的科興疫苗率先送俾香港人。"},{"pid":"f79d2d36fb027266772e1e9befd6b795f7601181","tid":2419753,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:04:02.000Z","msg":"y軸係咩嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276eaa6ae737c37a6830a3c64769efc2f6720bda","tid":2419753,"uid":38861,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"d975c693db248543c74662ca7ecfa737cff0d350","tid":2419753,"uid":34119,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:00:24.000Z","msg":"咁科興呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:04:40.000Z","msg":"慢功出細火，我哋依D重視效率同成效的香港人，係唔會明白中國人「百年磨一針」的情懷。<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4140f34c1bfa57ad13f851d72e1e3047e6b621df","tid":2419753,"uid":31254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T13:07:32.000Z","msg":"出邊成堆5毛洗地話mRNA影響幾十袋喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知佢哋Bio係邊個大師教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32aaf31ff912ad94904fe54eb140a9e6f02ef879","tid":2419753,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f79d2d36fb027266772e1e9befd6b795f7601181","tid":2419753,"uid":176447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0